<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark sticky-top">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <%= link_to "RubyTrivia", site_home_index_path, class: "navbar-brand" %>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
        </ul>
        
        <!-- Login links aligned to the right -->
        <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <%= link_to users_backoffice_home_index_path, class: "btn btn-outline-info my-2 my-sm-0 me-2" do %>
              <%= t('Login') %>
            <% end %>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-outline-info my-2 my-sm-0 me-2" do %>
              <%= t('Sign Up') %>
            <% end %>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav><br>

  <body>
    <main role="main">
      <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
      ================================================== -->
      <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

      <div class="container marketing">

      <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
      <div class="container">
        <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
        <div class="row text-white" style="height: 50vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
          <div class="col-lg-4 text-center mb-4">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="/assets/logo.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="280" height="280">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
            <h2 style="font-size: 2.5em; color: #333; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);">Ruby Trivia</h2>
            <p>Discover Ruby Trivia, an application by DevThree designed to assist new programmers in mastering Ruby on Rails. Visit
              <a href="http://www.devthree.com.br" class="text-white">www.devthree.com.br</a> to learn more about our mission and resources.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details Â»</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        </div><!-- /.row -->
      </div><!-- /.container -->



        <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

        <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

        <div class="row featurette text-white">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Free Ruby on Rails Learning Platform: Master the Framework</h2>
            <p class="lead">
                  Explore our free learning platform for mastering Ruby on Rails. Whether you're a beginner or
             an experienced developer, our comprehensive resources cover everything from fundamentals to advanced techniques.
              Dive into real-world projects, learn efficient development practices, and join a vibrant community of learners. 
              Start coding today and unleash the power of Rails to advance your career in tech</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="/assets/rails_free.png" alt="Rails Image" width="420" height="420">
          </div>
        </div>


        <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

        <div class="row featurette text-white">
          <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Ruby on Rails in Major Enterprises: Driving Efficiency and Innovation</h2>
            <p class="lead">
              Ruby on Rails (Rails) has become pivotal in enterprise software development for its simplicity,
             robustness, and agility. This framework accelerates time-to-market by emphasizing convention over configuration,
              making it ideal for scalable applications that evolve with enterprise growth. With a rich ecosystem of plugins
               and a developer-friendly codebase, Rails supports diverse enterprise needs from e-commerce to analytics, fostering
                collaboration and innovation. By adhering to DRY and MVC principles, Rails ensures code maintainability and scalability,
                 crucial for large-scale deployments. As enterprises prioritize agility and innovation, Rails continues to empower efficient,
                  scalable solutions that drive competitive advantage and exceptional user experiences.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="/assets/rails.jpg" alt="500x500" >
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

        <div class="row featurette text-white">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Sign in and Start Using the Tool Now!
            <p class="lead">Unlock your access to our powerful tool by signing in today. Dive into a wealth of resources 
            and features designed to enhance your experience from the moment you log in. Join a vibrant community of learners 
            and developers, ready to support your journey in mastering Ruby on Rails and beyond. </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="/assets/rails_login.png" alt="500x500" width="420" height="420" >
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

        <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

      </div><!-- /.container -->


      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <footer class="container text-center">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg">Back to top</a>
        <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">
      </footer>
      <footer class="container mt-4 text-white">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <form action="/send_email" method="POST">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" required>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email address</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send</button>
        </form>
      </footer>
    </main>

  <div class="container mt-4">
    <%= yield %>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
